Philosophy

Copy that earns trust first.

Most email agencies write for the open rate. We write for the relationship â€” because in regulated markets, a single overclaimed word can cost more than an entire campaign earns.

We believe the most commercially powerful email is also the most honest one. Compliance is not a constraint on creativity â€” it is the creative brief.

Pet wellness is a $150 billion global industry. The brands that win long-term are not the ones that shout the loudest. They are the ones that earn trust first, set expectations honestly, and build communities that buy again and again.

"The brand that tells the truth about what it cannot do builds more trust than the one that overclaims everything it can."
